The room kitchen bathroom everything is very good the main reason I give it three star rating is because of the transportation.  This transport facility is not suitable for us to go out.  There are three to four buses in the morning and three to four buses in the evening.  If anyone comes in between, they have to wait at the check point for at least five hours.  During this waiting time we cannot even go to use the restroom.  Walking is not allowed.  There is only one bus every three quarters of an hour.  Second, we do not receive any letter medicine directly, it only comes to the check post.  For that we have to ask the driver one day and go to the check point.  It will be very convenient for us if bus number 35 goes past the boat station and reaches the dormitory.
